src/
├── css/
├── fonts/
├── img/
├── partials/
├── public/
├── index.html
├── page-2.html
├── page-3.html
└── main.js


---

## ⚙️ Development

Install dependencies:


npm install


Run development server:


npm run dev


Build for production:


npm run build


---

## 📦 Deployment

The project is automatically deployed to GitHub Pages via GitHub Actions after pushing to the `main` branch.

